    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very sound, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience with a responsive engine and solid transmission. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of careful use, while the exterior retains a strong finish with just a few small, typical blemishes from regular road use. All major systems and features are fully functional, making this an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
